S'  This is the first of the proposed sets of notes to be published in the\nwebsite Gonit Sora (http://gonitsora.com). The notes will hopefully be able to\nhelp the students to learn their subject in an easy and comprehensible way.\nThese notes are aimed at mimicking exactly what would be typically taught in a\none-semester course at a college or university. The level of the notes would be\nroughly at the undergraduate level. The present sets of notes are not yet\ncomplete and this is the second version that is being posted. These notes\ncontain very few proofs and only state the important results in Probability\nTheory. These notes are based on the course taught at Tezpur University, Assam,\nIndia by Dr. Santanu Dutta. There may be some errors and typos in these notes\nwhich we hope the reader would bring to our notice.\n'
